{"word":"G184 - Ἀκελδαμά - Akeldamá - ak-el-dam-ah' - Aceldama","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">Ἀκελδαμά</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">Akeldamá</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak-el-dam-ah'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Aceldama</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Location / இடப்பெயர்</span>"},{"paragraph":"அக்கெல்தமா - ஓர் இடத்தின் பெயர்"},{"paragraph":"Akeldama"},{"paragraph":"\"இரத்த நிலம்\""},{"paragraph":"\"field of blood\""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of Chaldee origin (meaning <i>field of blood</i>; corresponding to [<a href=\"#/H2506 - חֵלֶק - chêleq - khay'lek/2506\">H2506</a>] and [<a href=\"#/H1818 - דָּם - dâm - dawm/1818\">H1818</a>]); <i>Akeldama</i>, a place near Jerusalem: - Aceldama.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}